data.description:
Brand new roof 30 year architectural shingles! HVAC only 3 years old, 2.4 acres, 25x25 WORKSHOP w/220/110 wiring plus water plumbed out.
Buyer to pick out paint color for living, dining and kitchen upon request.
3b2b home with 2 car garage. There are covenants without the HOA. This is a perfect home for your family. There is plenty of room for privacy and playing. The pantry is large and ready to store all of your goodies. Formal dining room for those special occasions with family and friends. Fireplace in the great room too cozy up to on those cold nights. Sitting area in master bedroom with double vanities, tub and walk in shower. Walk in master closet. The outdoor area is gorgeous with mature trees, a level lot, partial fenced yard, and covered back porch. Property is marked with metal stakes
